      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single displacement rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. No rate-variation study was performed. This factor is below the required level; the gap is accepted on the basis that F1717 is a quasi-static standard and rate sensitivity for titanium constructs at this regime is negligible per published literature, but the limitation is acknowledged."
