    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted on the basis of negligible rate sensitivity for quasi-static titanium construct testing under ASTM F1717. All three primary QoIs satisfy the quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percentage difference < 10%) across N=11 specimens and two independent laboratories. The FEA modeling framework is assessed as sufficiently credible for the stated COU.",
